{"prompt": "Generate a sleek website for a venture capital firm. The brand color should be a sophisticated navy blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Venture Capital Firm</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #0a1f33; /* Sophisticated Navy Blue */\n            --secondary-color: #1a3a5a; /* Slightly lighter navy */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --secondary-text-color: #cccccc;\n            --accent-color: #4CAF50; /* A subtle green for CTAs */\n            --font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: var(--font-family);\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            scroll-behavior: smooth;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 50px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            position: sticky;\n            top: 0;\n            z-index: 1000;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero {\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 0;\n            background: linear-gradient(rgba(10, 31, 51, 0.8), rgba(10, 31, 51, 0.9)), url('https://via.placeholder.com/1500x800/0a1f33/ffffff?text=Venture+Capital+Image') no-repeat center center/cover;\n            min-height: 60vh;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        #hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #hero p {\n            font-size: 1.4em;\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n            max-width: 700px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--accent-color);\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;\n            display: inline-block;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #388E3C; /* Darker green on hover */\n            transform: translateY(-2px);\n        }\n\n        #about, #investments, #contact {\n            padding: 80px 0;\n        }\n\n        #about h2, #investments h2, #contact h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        #about p, #contact p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n            line-height: 1.7;\n            text-align: center;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto 40px auto;\n        }\n\n        .investment-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 30px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .investment-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .investment-card h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n        }\n\n        .investment-card p {\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n            font-size: 1em;\n            line-height: 1.5;\n            text-align: left;\n            max-width: unset;\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .investment-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.5em;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1.2em;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                margin: 0 10px;\n            }\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 480px) {\n            header h1 {\n                font-size: 1.8em;\n            }\n            nav {\n                display: flex;\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n                padding-top: 10px;\n            }\n            nav a {\n                margin: 5px 0;\n            }\n            #hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2em;\n            }\n            #hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            .cta-button {\n                padding: 10px 20px;\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>[Your Firm Name]</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About Us</a>\n                <a href=\"#investments\">Investments</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section id=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Fueling Innovation, Driving Growth.</h2>\n            <p>We are a forward-thinking venture capital firm dedicated to identifying and nurturing disruptive technologies and visionary founders.</p>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Connect With Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>About Us</h2>\n            <p>At [Your Firm Name], we leverage deep industry expertise, a robust network, and a data-driven approach to partner with ambitious companies. Our mission is to provide not just capital, but strategic guidance and operational support to help our portfolio companies achieve market leadership and create lasting value.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"investments\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Focus Areas</h2>\n            <div class=\"investment-grid\">\n                <div class=\"investment-card\">\n                    <h3>FinTech</h3>\n                    <p>Transforming financial services with innovative solutions.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"investment-card\">\n                    <h3>SaaS</h3>\n                    <p>Empowering businesses through scalable software platforms.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"investment-card\">\n                    <h3>AI & Machine Learning</h3>\n                    <p>Pioneering the future with intelligent systems.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"investment-card\">\n                    <h3>Biotechnology</h3>\n                    <p>Advancing health and wellness through cutting-edge science.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n            <p>Interested in partnering with us or learning more about our investment philosophy? We'd love to hear from you.</p>\n            <a href=\"mailto:info@yourfirm.com\" class=\"cta-button\" style=\"background-color: var(--accent-color); color: var(--primary-color);\">Email Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 [Your Firm Name]. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Optional: Add smooth scrolling for navigation links\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}